{"tid":1089213,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"［JJ插沙求救］懷疑買到假iPhone","createTime":"2019-04-02T15:22:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-04T16:00:22.000Z","uid":147057,"like":2,"dislike":55,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"2c5f7aeaac4008108cd6b5e45561473e3690d79e","tid":1089213,"uid":147057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T15:22:37.000Z","msg":"啱啱係dcfever買左部二手Space Grey iPhone 8<br />\n佢聲稱係港行256GB<br />\n當時淨係Check左機身，功能，對下IMEI同Model Number就算數<br />\n翻倒黎發現個盒有啲唔對路 而且入面啲配件都唔似原廠嘢<br />\n之後就好似上網做Research<br />\n<br />\n睇翻部機個Model Number係MG6Q2ZP/A<br />\n而我去查呢一個Model Number搵到既係星加坡既Space Grey iPhone 8 64GB<br />\n香港行貨既Space Grey 256GB應該係MQ7F2ZP/A先啱<br />\n<br />\n唔知係我ON9怪錯好人定係我真係中伏啦<br />\n我都知買二手中伏係我抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係就算中伏 我都唔想條仆街繼續逍遙法外<br />\n宜家WhatsApp左佢冇覆到 打算聽日去報警<br />\n唔知搞唔搞得掂呢？<br />\n<br />\n有佢電話 有對話紀錄 有佢個賣物Post既Description<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vf0xXA8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVf0xXA8.jpg&h=41ab2df2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港行機 上面肯定有中文字 唔會純英文<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SXTvKgj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSXTvKgj.jpg&h=6bc4eb08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nModel Number已經有古怪<br />\nIMEI條Barcode位仲要印左啲字係度<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p1bECBH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp1bECBH.png&h=04443269&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n機內About Phone Cap圖"},{"pid":"35564316fd22d6c3c61816fa99b639f29f5b1cf7","tid":1089213,"uid":85659,"like":62,"dislike":1,"score":61,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T15:28:37.000Z","msg":"Jj插沙圖呢"},{"pid":"b628b0656a4d0d679f53311a11739c86eec6ba56","tid":1089213,"uid":147057,"like":23,"dislike":2,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T15:29:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Hferxz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Hfer